nf_ingredient_statement:
Whole Grain Oats, Whole Grain Corn, Sugar, Fructose, Rice Flour, Palm Oil, Corn Starch, Dried Strawberry Puree, Corn Syrup, Dextrose, Canola Oil, Salt, Baking Soda, Natural Flavor, Caramel Color. Vitamin E (mixed tocopherols) and BHT Added to Preserve Freshness.

Vitamins and Minerals: Tricalcium Phosphate, Zinc and Iron (mineral nutrients), Vitamin C (sodium ascorbate), A B Vitamin (niacinamide), Vitamin B6 (pyridoxine hydrochloride), Vitamin B2 (riboflavinn), Vitamin B1 (thiamin mononitrate), Vitamin A (palmitate), A B Vitamin (folic acid), Vitamin B12, Vitamin D3.
